title: Lactation Machinations (New Stories, Old Friends #1) - Sophie Si
description:
Harry and Larry's Porn Circus gets crazy when a huge breasted Jenny Good comes with her mounds loaded to the brim with delicious dirty milk. Electrical appliances, gigantic members and a particularly crazy insertion aside, this is all about seeing just how far those mega-hooters can squirt a white line. All action, all hardcore!

This is the first book in the New Stories, Old Friends series. You can find the next story, The Russian Affair, at your favorite e-store or get all four stories in The New Stories, Old Friends Collection.

Thanks for reading!
